"title": "4065: orderliness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4065: orderliness",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>In his creating, sustaining and saving work, God reveals himself as a God of order. Likewise, the life of his people and of society as a whole should be orderly.</p>\n<h2>Orderliness in creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:12\">ISA 45:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:31\">GEN 1:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job26:7-Job26:10\">JOB 26:7–26:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:4-Job38:11\">JOB 38:4–38:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:3\">PSA 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1\">PSA 19:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:5-Ps104:9\">PSA 104:5–104:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:26\">ISA 40:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:26\">ACT 17:26</a></p>\n<h2>Orderliness in providence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:22\">GEN 8:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps65:9\">PSA 65:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:14-Ps104:27\">PSA 104:14–104:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:15\">PSA 145:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a></p>\n<h2>Orderliness in salvation</h2>\n<h3>Salvation was planned by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:29\">ROM 8:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:7\">1CO 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:4-Eph1:5\">EPH 1:4–1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:9\">2TI 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:2\">TIT 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:2\">1PE 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:8\">REV 13:8</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's coming was prepared in advance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:26-Luke24:27\">LUK 24:26–24:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:46\">JHN 5:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:18\">ACT 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:4\">GAL 4:4</a></p>\n<h2>Orderliness in the life of God's people</h2>\n<h3>Corporate worship must be orderly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:9\">EXO 25:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:40\">1CO 14:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:12\">1CH 28:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:44\">ACT 7:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:32-1Cor14:33\">1CO 14:32–14:33</a></p>\n<h3>Personal devotion includes orderliness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:6\">1TH 5:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:28\">PRO 25:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:13\">ROM 13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:17\">1CO 7:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:16\">EPH 5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:2-1Tim3:5\">1TI 3:2–3:5</a></p>\n<h3>Respect for leaders as part of God's order</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:28\">EXO 22:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:17\">HEB 13:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:6\">1SA 24:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:17\">1TI 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:7\">HEB 13:7</a></p>\n<h3>Order in pastoral care</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:28\">1CO 12:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:5\">TIT 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:3\">ACT 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:23\">ACT 14:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:4-Rom12:8\">ROM 12:4–12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:11\">EPH 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:10\">1PE 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:1-1Pet5:3\">1PE 5:1–5:3</a></p>\n<h2>Orderliness in society</h2>\n<h3>God gives responsibility in his administration to men and women</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:6\">PSA 82:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:2-Dan6:7\">DAN 6:2–6:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1\">ROM 13:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:1\">TIT 3:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:13-1Pet2:14\">1PE 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h3>Governing authorities are ordained by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1\">ROM 13:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:11\">JHN 19:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:6\">ROM 13:6</a></p>\n<h3>Those in authority are to be honoured</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:1\">TIT 3:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:21\">MAT 22:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:17\">MRK 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:25\">LUK 20:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:1-1Tim2:2\">1TI 2:1–2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:13\">1PE 2:13</a></p>\n<h3>Order in the home and workplace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:4\">1TI 3:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:14\">EXO 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:12\">EXO 20:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:13\">1SA 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:5\">JOB 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:1\">EPH 6:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:5\">EPH 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:4\">1TI 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:12\">1TI 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:1\">1TI 6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:6\">TIT 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:4-Titus2:5\">TIT 2:4–2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:9-Titus2:10\">TIT 2:9–2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:18\">1PE 2:18</a></p>",
